And, as I was looking
through your book,

00:04:03.850 --> 00:04:06.349
I noted that you had
a passage about how

00:04:06.349 --> 00:04:07.890
the ties that you
do wear when you do

00:04:07.890 --> 00:04:11.080
wear a tie are all designed
actually by your wife.

00:04:11.080 --> 00:04:12.330
RICHARD DAWKINS: That is true.

00:04:12.330 --> 00:04:13.480
She paints silk.

00:04:13.480 --> 00:04:17.774
So every one of my ties
is a one-off unique tie.

