00:23:56.208 --> 00:23:57.011
[LAUGHTER]

00:23:57.011 --> 00:23:58.636
RICHARD DAWKINS:
False memory syndrome.

00:23:58.636 --> 00:23:58.980
MALE SPEAKER: Right.

00:23:58.980 --> 00:23:59.160
RICHARD DAWKINS: Yeah.

00:23:59.160 --> 00:24:01.700
MALE SPEAKER: And I had
